<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3143271" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="U" oldref="10">Typeface</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3155922" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="11"><ahelp hid="SVX_COMBOBOX_RID_SVXPAGE_CHAR_NAME_LB_CTL_STYLE">Select the formatting that you want to apply.</ahelp></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3152361" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="42">You can also use the <emph>Typeface </emph>icons on the <emph>Object Bar</emph>.</paragraph>
